        </p>
        <p>
          <a
            target="_blank"
            href="https://docs.google.com/document/d/1SAq-EhaEDn2x1cjadhp95rr8ga_S_DlFthl83DtdTn4/edit?usp=sharing"
            class="font-semibold hover:underline"
          >
            Get my CV
          </a>
        </p>
      </div>
      <p class="font-semibold">Feel free to reach out to me on social media!</p>
      <div class="flex gap-8">
        <a href="https://github.com/LukePetko">
          <img src="/github.svg" class="h-16 w-16" />
        </a>
        <a href="https://twitter.com/LUkEPetko">
          <img src="/x.svg" class="h-16" />
        </a>
        <a href="https://linkedin.com/in/lukas-petko">
          <img src="/linkedin.svg" class="h-16" />
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="md:w-1/3">
      <Image
        class="shadow-[10px_10px_0px_0px] shadow-white transition-shadow duration-300 hover:shadow-[20px_20px_0px_0px]"
