  <h2 class="mt-10 font-display text-6xl font-bold md:mt-0">Experience</h2>
  <div class="flex flex-col gap-12 pb-12">
    <div
      class="ml-3 flex flex-col gap-2 border-l-2 border-dashed pl-3 md:ml-12 md:pl-12"
    >
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold">AKULAR</h2>
      <p class="text-lg font-semibold">Lead Full-stack Engineer</p>
      <p class="text-base">Aug 2024 - Present</p>
      <p class="text-xl">
        Recently, I moved into the position of Lead Full-stack Engineer. I am
        responsible for developing both the frontend and backend of the
        application, as well as integrating it with backend services.
        Additionally, I manage task prioritization, time estimation, code
        reviews, and ensure that the codebase remains clean and maintainable.
      </p>
      <p class="mt-6 text-lg font-semibold">Full-stack Engineer</p>
      <p class="text-base">Jun 2022 - Aug 2024</p>
      <p class="text-xl">
        In my most recent role, which I began while still pursuing my university
        studiesâ€”a commitment I maintain to this dayâ€”I specialize in developing
        an application focused on the visualization of digital twins in
        construction. My work primarily involves utilizing React, TypeScript,
        Material-UI (MUI), and GraphQL, with integration into AWS for cloud
        services and Hasura for efficient data management. This role allows me
        to contribute significantly to the innovative field of construction
        visualization, leveraging advanced technologies to enhance user
        experience and data interaction.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div
      class="mr-3 flex flex-col gap-2 border-r-2 border-dashed pr-3 md:mr-12 md:pr-12"
    >
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold">
        Faculty of Informatics and Information Technologies<br />Slovak
        University of Technology
      </h2>
      <p class="text-lg font-semibold">Teaching Assistant</p>
      <p class="text-base">Sep 2023 - Feb 2024</p>
      <p class="text-xl">
        In my next position, while continuing my studies, I took on the role of
        instructing JavaScript to fellow university students at my alma mater.
        This opportunity allowed me to share my expertise and enthusiasm for
        programming, enhancing my pedagogical skills and reinforcing my
        understanding of JavaScript fundamentals within an academic setting.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div
      class="ml-3 flex flex-col gap-2 border-l-2 border-dashed pl-3 md:ml-12 md:pl-12"
    >
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold">PosAm</h2>
      <p class="text-lg font-semibold">Junior Deleloper</p>
      <p class="text-base">Feb 2021 - Jun 2022</p>
      <p class="text-xl">
        During my university studies, I started a position where I continued to
        harness Angular for development purposes. Additionally, I expanded my
        technical repertoire by writing automated tests using Robot Framework.
        This role was instrumental in the development of a project for a power
        plant, allowing me to contribute significantly while enhancing my skills
        in both front-end development and quality assurance.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div
      class="mr-3 flex flex-col gap-2 border-r-2 border-dashed pr-3 md:mr-12 md:pr-12"
    >
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold">Asseco Central Europe</h2>
      <p class="text-lg font-semibold">Junior Delevoper</p>
      <p class="text-base">Jun 2019 - Aug 2019</p>
      <p class="text-xl">
        Following my high school graduation, I started on an internship where I
        focused on developing a banking application using Angular. This
        experience allowed me to apply and enhance my programming skills in a
        real-world financial technology environment, contributing to projects
        while gaining valuable industry knowledge.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div
      class="ml-3 flex flex-col gap-2 border-l-2 border-dashed pl-3 md:ml-12 md:pl-12"
    >
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold">FullEye</h2>
      <p class="text-lg font-semibold">VR Unity Developer</p>
      <p class="text-base">Jun 2018 - Aug 2018</p>
      <p class="text-xl">
        During my internship at FullEye, I focused on developing immersive VR
        applications using the Unity framework. My work involved designing and
        implementing interactive 3D environments and user interfaces for virtual
        reality experiences, enhancing the overall user engagement and
        interactivity of the applications.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <h2 class="font-display text-6xl font-bold">Education</h2>
  <div class="flex flex-col gap-12 pb-12">
    <div
      class="ml-3 flex flex-col gap-2 border-l-2 border-dashed pl-3 md:ml-12 md:pl-12"
    >
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold">
        Faculty of Informatics and Information Technologies<br />Slovak
        University of Technology
      </h2>
      <p class="text-lg font-semibold">Master's degree, Computer Science</p>
      <p class="text-base">2022 - 2024</p>
      <p class="text-xl">
        I completed my Master's studies in Computer Science at the Faculty of
        Informatics and Information Technologies (FIIT) at the Slovak University
        of Technology. My academic focus included advanced topics in networking,
        distributed systems, and software engineering. For my thesis, I
        researched the virtualization of personal access points within the IEEE
        802.11 standard, aiming to improve network flexibility and efficiency.
      </p>
      <p class="text-lg font-semibold">Bachelor's degree, Informatics</p>
      <p class="text-base">2019 - 2022</p>
      <p class="text-xl">
        I completed my Bachelor studies at the Faculty of Informatics and
        Information Technologies (FIIT) at the Slovak University of Technology,
        delving into Data Structures and Algorithms (DSA), Object-Oriented
        Programming (OOP) principles, and the basics of software architecture.
        My academic work led to the development of a React Native application,
        titled 'Mobile Application for Sharing Traveling Safety Information,'
        which aims to enhance the safety and connectivity of friends and family
        during their travels.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</PageLayout>
